description:
Will we find out who was behind the Supreme Court leak on the Dobbs decision? Bannon perp-walked in NY echoes John Paul Jones, saying "I have not begun to fight." Will Biden Regime indict Trump? Are you Buck Sexton? Are you Clay Travis? Well, it depends. Steve Hilton of Fox News joins Clay and Buck to discuss the significance of Queen Elizabeth II and why the left hates her. Duke issues social justice, virtue signaling, gobbledygook statement on the BYU investigation of hoax racism accusation.
